e%20market%20for%20legal%20information%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20LexisNexis%20data%20baked%20into%20its%20interface%2C%20Harvey%20has%20a%20stronger%20case%20to%20make%20to%20law%20firms%20and%20a%20better%20shot%20at%20defending%20its%20early%20lead%20in%20the%20legal%20tech%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202022%2C%20Harvey%20shot%20to%20stardom%20in%20the%20legal%20tech%20space%20with%20backing%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20Sequoia.%20Today%2C%20over%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20country's%20100%20largest%20law%20firms%20count%20themselves%20as%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERopes%20%26amp%3B%20Gray%20%E2%80%94%20the%20seventh%20highest-grossing%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20rolled%20out%20Harvey%20firmwide%20in%20June%20after%20a%20year%20of%20use%20with%20a%20smaller%20test%20group%2C%20according%20to%20Ed%20Black%2C%20the%20firm's%20technology%20strategy%20leader.%20This%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paulweiss.com%2Finsights%2Ffirm-news%2Fpaul-weiss-partners-with-harvey-ai-on-new-ai-workflows-innovation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaul%20Weiss%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcing%20it%20co-developed%20a%20custom%20workflow%20builder%20with%20Harvey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20moves%20reflect%20a%20broader%20trend%20in%20Big%20Law%20as%20more%20firms%20shift%20from%20cautious%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-ai-tech-boom-bubble-fear-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epilot%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20full-scale%20deployments.%20The%20change%20could%20ratchet%20up%20pressure%20on%20startups%20like%20Harvey%2C%20Legora%2C%20Hebbia%2C%20and%20Eudia%2C%20all%20vying%20for%20the%20same%20budgets%20and%20attention%20from%20top%20firms%20and%20legal%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20CEO%20of%20LexisNexis%20North%20America%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Ireland%2C%20said%20the%20idea%20for%20the%20partnership%20came%20from%20customers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20toggling%20between%20the%2