%3Cli%3EWarren%20built%20an%20annex%20in%20the%20backyard%20where%20her%20daughter%20lives%20with%20her%20partner%20and%20baby.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sacha%20Warren%20from%20Surrey%2C%20England.%20Warren's%20financials%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20my%20house%20in%20Epsom%2C%20a%20town%20outside%20London%2C%20in%202001.%20It%20has%20a%20huge%20garden%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I'd%20never%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20lucky%20to%20get%20on%20the%20property%20ladder.%20My%20dad%20gave%20me%20the%20deposit%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%201997.%20UK%20property%20prices%20surged%20around%20that%20time%2C%20so%20when%20I%20sold%20it%2C%20I%20got%20a%20healthy%20deposit%20for%20this%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20a%20developer%20approached%20me%20about%20buying%20part%20of%20my%20land%20and%20putting%20two%20bungalows%20at%20the%20end%20of%20my%20garden.%20I%20loved%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20mortgage-free%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20but%20they%20couldn't%20get%20permission%20to%20build%20because%20of%20access%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ae794ce-a279-43be-b38e-56a5cb18e808%5C%22%3EFamily%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20garden%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20daughter%20started%20showing%20me%20videos%20of%20people%20building%20loft%20conversions%20or%20annexes.%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20to%20even%20consider%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20my%20daughter%2C%20who%20is%20now%2022%2C%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20got%20pregnant.%20They%20were%20living%20with%20us%20and%20paying%20%C2%A3350%20a%20month%20in%20rent.%20We%20had%20the%20space%2C%20but%20it%20was%20important%20for%20them%20to%20be%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20to%20think%20more%20seriously%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20an%20annex.%20My%20daughter%20and%20I%20are%20close%2C%20and%20I%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20all%20being%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20property%20in%20the%20area%20is%20ridiculous.%20Worrying%20about%20my%20daughter%20having%20a%20big%20mortgage%20kept%20me%20up%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20researching%20annexes%20and%20found%20a%20local%20company.%20It%20would%20be%20a%20quick%20build%20and%20meant%20my%20daughter%20and%20her%20partner%20could%20get%20established%20as%20their%20own%20family%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20an%20eight-month%20waiting%20list%2C%20but%20that%20gave%20me%20time%20to%20organize%20my%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226474f31d-ad1c-455d-bfad-38035f3fc041%5C%22%3EFinancing%20the%20project%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20paid%20off%20my%20mortgage%20in%202018%20when%20the%20equity%20in%20my%20parents'%20home%20was%20released%2C%20and%20they%20gave%20it%20to%20me%20as%20an%20early%20inheritance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20out%20a%2020-year%20mortgage%20loan%20on%20my%20house%20last%20year%20to%20help%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20annex.%20I%20agreed%20with%20my%20daughter%20that%20they%20would%20cover%20this%20monthly%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mortgage%20repayments%20are%20locked%20in%20for%20five%20years%20at%205.5%25.%20They%20pay%20me%20%C2%A3700%20a%20month%2C%20or%20about%20%24950%2C%20including%20utility%20bills.%20If%20they%20were%20paying%20rent%20on%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20here%2C%20they%20could%20be%20paying%20twice%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20never%20discussed%20a%20contract.%20In%20my%20will%2C%20my%20daughter%20is%20the%20sole%20beneficiary%20of%20my%20estate.%20We%20earn%20the%20same%2C%20and%20she%20completely%20understands%20the%20importance%20of%20earning%20money%20and%20paying%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20want%20to%20move%20out%2C%20I'll%20make%20the%20payments%20as%20the%20mortgage%20is%20in%20my%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225447bcf3-b1c9-451c-9022-7cc2447ebff1%5C%22%3EThe%202-bedroom%20annex%20layout%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20a%20prefabricated%2C%20two-bedroom%20annex%20with%20a%20bathroom%2C%20open%20plan%20kitchen%2C%20and%20lounge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20could%20choose%20options%20for%20each%20room.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20stressful%2C%20but%20it%20was%20enjoyable.%20The%20company%20did%20everything%20for%20us.%20They%20even%20applied%20for%20permission%20to%20build%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20needed%20to%20install%20water%20and%20electricity%2C%20but%20they%20were%20able%20to%20connect%20them%20to%20our%20mains%20supply.%20We%20installed%20a%20meter%20in%20case%20we%20rent%20the%20annex%20out%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20build%20took%20six%20weeks%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annex%20needs%20to%20be%20repainted%20every%20six%20years%2C%20and%20the%20sewage%20system%20costs%20%C2%A3750%20a%20year%20to%20maintain.%20My%20daughter%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20put%20money%20aside%20each%20month%20for%20when%20the%20bill%20comes%20through.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261b0fe92-4241-4d9e-88af-ad9ba4097eb4%5C%22%3ESharing%20the%20property%20is%20a%20slice%20of%20heaven%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20gave%20birth%20in%20January%202024%2C%20and%20they%20moved%20into%20the%20annex%20in%20September.%20We%20wanted%20them%20to%20be%20settled%20in%20it%20before%20the%20baby%20arrived%2C%20but%20it%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20really%20special%20time%20sharing%20our%20grandson's%20early%20days%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we'll%20send%20each%20other%20WhatsApps%2C%20and%20if%20I'm%20sitting%20on%20the%20patio%2C%20my%20daughter%20or%20her%20boyfriend%20might%20come%20out%20to%20chat%20or%20socialize.%20We%20don't%20tiptoe%20around%20each%20other.%20They%20do%20their%20own%20food%20shopping%2C%20but%20if%20one%20of%20us%20makes%20too%20much%20food%2C%20we'll%20share%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20as%20a%20dementia%20care%20assistant%20