51c1b961d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221833%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReal%20estate%20investor%20and%20entrepreneur%20Jeremy%20Barker%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Murphy%20Door.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jeremy%20Barker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJeremy%20Barker%20started%20a%20hidden%20door%20company%2C%20Murphy%20Door%2C%20to%20supplement%20his%20firefighter%20income.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20grew%20rapidly%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20look%20into%20large%20commercial%20spaces.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20bought%20a%20%243%20million%20building%20with%20just%20%2430%2C000%20of%20his%20own%20money%20and%20expanded%20his%20portfolio%20from%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Barker%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20career%20bouncing%20between%20construction%2C%20working%20as%20a%20paramedic%20and%20as%20a%20fireman%2C%20as%20well%20as%20experimenting%20with%20start-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kind%20of%20played%20ping%20pong%20for%20the%20first%2035%20years%2C%20trying%20to%20decide%20what%20it%20is%20that%20I%20loved%2C%20which%20was%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20it%20doesn't%20pay.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20live%20on%20%241%2C600%20take-home%20a%20month.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnwilling%20to%20give%20up%20his%20firefighter%20career%20completely%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20supplement%20the%20modest%20salary%20with%20a%20side%20hustle.%20He%20started%20making%20hinges%20for%20hidden%20doors%20%E2%80%94%20an%20idea%20inspired%20by%20a%20DIY%20home%20theater%20project%20for%20his%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20and%20called%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmurphydoor.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMurphy%20Door%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20escalated%20quickly%20from%202013%20into%202016%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20signed%20Home%20Depot.%20It%20just%20grew%20really%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Murphy%20Door%20created%20an%20additional%20revenue%20stream%2C%20he%20put%20most%20of%20the%20profit%20back%20into%20the%20business.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20he%20stumbled%20into%20real%20estate%20that%20his%20wealth%20started%20to%20snowball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234bc6e31-4f6b-4310-b2b6-d20d0e4a7d2b%5C%22%3EFinancing%20a%20%243%20million%20space%20with%20%2430%2C000%20in%20savings%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20his%20primary%20home%20in%20Utah%2C%20Barker%20had%20no%20experience%20buying%20real%20estate.%20But%20as%20Murphy%20Door%20took%20off%20and%20outgrew%20its%20original%20space%2C%20he%20and%20his%20real%20estate%20agent%20started%20looking%20at%20larger%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20agent%20found%20a%20deal%20on%20a%2090%2C000-square-foot%20building%20that%20he%20told%20Barker%20was%20too%20good%20to%20pass%20up%2C%20and%20pitched%20it%20as%20a%20space%20the%20company%20could%20grow%20into.%20It%20was%20listed%20for%20%243%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20looked%20at%20him%20and%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Are%20you%20freaking%20crazy%3F%20%243%20million%3F%20I%20work%20at%20a%20fire%20department.%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20get%20a%20loan.%20My%20mortgage%20was%20difficult%20enough%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Barker.%20%26quot%3BHe%20goes%2C%20'You%20sign%20this%20LOI.%20I'll%20help%20you%20figure%20out%20the%20money.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20Barker%20turned%20to%20YouTube%20to%20learn%20about%20financing%20commercial%20real%20estate.%20He%20learned%20a%20couple%20of%20things%3A%20One%2C%20he'd%20need%20to%20raise%20capital.%20His%20%2430%2C000%20in%20savings%20was%20a%20start%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20for%20a%20down%20payment.%20Two%2C%20he%20could%20lease%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20space%2C%20about%2070%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20that%20he%20didn't%20need%20for%20Murphy%20Door.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20understood%20how%20letters%20of%20intent%20(LOIs)%20and%20purchase%20and%20sale%20agreements%20(PSAs)%20worked%2C%20he%20realized%20he%20could%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20time%20between%20signing%20one%20and%20the%20closing%20date%20to%20get%20a%20head%20start%20on%20leasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20back-and-forth%20with%20the%20seller%20regarding%20terms%2C%20he%20got%20the%20green%20light%20to%20list%20the%20building%20for%20lease%20before%20closing%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20sell%20them%20a%20little%20bit.%20I%20said%2C%20'Look%2C%20I%20only%20use%20a%20small%20space%2C%20but%20if%20I%20could%20put%20it%20up%20for%20lease%2C%20you're%20not%20committed%20to%20anything.%20I'll%20let%20everybody%20know%20early%20that%20it's%20not%20bought%20yet%2C%20but%20there's%20a%2090%25%20chance%20it%20closes.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20signed%20the%20PSA%2C%20put%20a%20'for%20lease'%20sign%20outside%20the%20building%2C%20and%2C%20%26quot%3Bwithin%2024%20hours%2C%20I%20had%20my%20first%20tenant%20that%20was%20like%2022%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWithin%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20I%20got%20another%20big%20tenant%2C%20and%20before%20I%20closed%2C%20I%20had%20a%20full%20package%20of%20lease%20rent%20roll%20equivalent%20to%20about%20%24140%2C000%20at%20that%20time%20annually%20in%20that%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lease%20agreements%20helped%20him%20secure%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20capital%20he%20needed%20%E2%80%94%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20thousand%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20down%20payment%2C%20as%20he%20was%20able%20to%20show%20investors%20the%20expected%20NOI.%20It%20also%20helped%20secure%20a%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20back%20to%20Bank%20of%20Utah%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20'Here%20are%20my%20rent%20rolls.'%20They%20did%20the%20first%20mortgage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWithin%2012%20months%2C%20I%20retabled%20it%20over%20to%20Golden%20West%20Credit%20Union%20and%20pulled%20%242%20million%20out%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'd%20only%20put%20in%20%2430%2C000.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20paid%20his%20investors%20back%20within%2024%20months%2C%20and%20the%20building's%20value%20has%20more%20than%20quadrupled%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecognizing%20the%20tremendous%20wealth-building%20opportunity%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20from%20there%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20rinsed%20and%20repeated%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barker.%20He's%20fine-tuned%20his%20strategy%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20dissimilar%20to%20his%20first%20deal%3A%20Find%20an%20overlooked%20or%20undervalued%20property%20%E2%80%94%20ideally%20a%20building%20that%20has%20been%20on%20the%20market%20for%20years%20in%20order%20to%20gain%20negotiation%20leverage%20%E2%80%94%20and%20build%20a%20long%20enough%20closing%20period%20into%20the%20terms%20with%20the%20seller%20in%20order%20to%20have%20time%20to%20set%20up%20lease%20agreements%20with%20future%20tenants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20June%202025%2C%20Barker%20owns%20more%20than%2030%20commercial%20and%20residential%20properties.%20BI%20confirmed%20his%20ownership%20by%20reviewing%20his%202024%20property%20tax%20notices%20and%20his%20lease%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jeremy%20barker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6851bf2c85e81483682c45d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222276%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBarker%20and%20his%20family%20reside%20in%20Utah.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jeremy%20Barker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ecd35cbf-1129-47b0-a72b-ab0bce84f5de%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20get%20started%20in%20real%20estate%20with%20little%20to%20no%20savings%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%2C%20who%20said%20he%20faced%20bankruptcy%20twice%20early%20in%20his%20career%2C%20didn't%20have%20much%20savings%20to%20work%20with%20when%20he%20started%20buying%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20I%20had%20to%20think%20outside%20the%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20What%20he%20didn't%20have%20in%20capital%2C%20he%20made%20up%20for%20in%20research.%20His%20edge%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20would%20be%20understanding%20his%20market%20better%20than%20anyone%20else%2C%20and%20using%20that%20knowledge%20to%20pitch%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpend%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20time%20understanding%20the%20marketplace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20learned%20about%20buildings.%20I%20learned%20what%20rent%20goes%20for%20around%20here.%20And%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20get%20complicated.%20I'm%20looking%20at%3A%20What%20is%20the%20average%20rent%20rate%3F%20OK%2C%20it's%20going%20for%20%2412%20to%20%2415%20a%20square%20foot.%20If%20I%20buy%20this%20property%2C%20my%20hard%20costs%20are%20going%20to%20be%20%244%20a%20square%20foot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20find%20a%20deal%20that%20you're%20confident%20will%20work%2C%20start%20pitching%20to%20any%20potential%20investors%20within%20your%20networks.%20He'd%20frame%20it%20as%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20any%20money%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20table%2C%20but%20you%20have%20all%20my%20time.%20I'm%20willing%20to%20give%20away%20X%25%20of%20the%20equity%20to%20just%20pull%20off%20my%20first%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPitch%20with%20confidence%2C%20not%20arrogance%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20understand%20the%20market%20really%20well%20and%20talk%20at%20a%20super%20basic%20level%2C%20not%20to%20sound%20like%20you're%20smarter%20than%20you%20are.%20Just%20be%20confident.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20talk%20outside%20your%20scope.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%20says%20he%20reached%20financial%20independence%20years%20ago%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20real%20estate%20portfolio%2C%20which%20brings%20in%20about%20%242.5%20million%20in%20annual%20revenue.%20It's%20freed%20him%20up%20to%20spend%20his%20time%20exactly%20how%20he%20wants%3A%20in%20the%20fire%20department%2C%20where%20he%20still%20works%20part-time%2C%20and%20at%20Murphy%20Door.%3C%2