d-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhumsafar.org%2Fcontact-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Naz%20Foundation%20(India)%20Trust%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201994%20by%20Anjali%20Gopalan%2C%20Naz%20Foundation%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20advancing%20LGBTQIA%2B%20rights%20in%20India%2C%20including%20leading%20the%202009%20legal%20battle%20that%20first%20struck%20down%20Section%20377.%20Alongside%20legal%20advocacy%2C%20it%20provides%20counselling%2C%20peer%20support%20groups%2C%20medical%20and%20legal%20referrals%2C%20and%20home-based%20care%20for%20people%20living%20with%20HIV%2FAIDS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20LGBTQIA%2B%20initiative%20has%20provided%20face%E2%80%91to%E2%80%91face%20and%20tele%E2%80%91counselling%2C%20medical%20referrals%2C%20home%E2%80%91based%20care%20for%20families%2C%20and%20outreach%20on%20safe%E2%80%91sex%2C%20stigma%20and%20coming%E2%80%91out%20%E2%80%94%20reaching%20over%20234%2C000%20individuals%20to%20date%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20youth-focused%20sports%20programmes%2C%20vocational%20training%2C%20and%20peer%20education%20initiatives%20help%20build%20confidence%20and%20create%20safe%20spaces%20for%20LGBTQIA%2B%20individuals%20across%20the%20country.%20A%20nationwide%20helpline%20(%2B91%208800329176%20%2F%20%2B91%20(011)%2047504630)%20further%20extends%20emotional%20and%20mental%20health%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nazindia.org%2Fcontact%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg